latestIgtvVideos.title: Part -(2) &tv channel 👉 Ek Mahanayak - B.R Ambedkar 👉 Shabnam
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
When I was selected for this character, I was stressed out to play the role. Many questions gathered my mind, will I be able to fulfill what the director "demands". But I am happy to see  that I  not only carried this character gracefully but also performed it accurate and it was appreciated by all. Shabnam Bai is a negative character. According to one's perspective it is very easy to play negative character but it's not.Playing negative character is alot tricky yet creative but also difficult to play, because there are so many twists and emotions you have to show through just expressions.I have the blessings of my God &  my parents and the support of my husband.
Special thanks to the Director Vinod Manikrao and  @incognit0.96 - Creative head 
Special thanks :- @andtvofficial Note :- THIS WAS AN ACT NO BODY WAS HURTED DURING THE SEEN (SHOOTING)
